	<h1 class="title">爱奇艺和狮门影业合作，很多好莱坞大片只有在它那儿看</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4369/small/4369.jpg?1419239008" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">晏文静 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-11 08:15:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15905/medium/15905.jpg?1444460814" alt="" />			
	</div>
